/*
  Cleaned & optimized Data Logger sketch
  - 12 x DS18B20 (each on separate pin)
  - 4  x DHT22
  - LCD I2C 20x4 (0x27)
  - RTC DS1307 (RtcDS1307)
  - SD logging via SdFat (SoftSpi CS pin:10)
  - LED pin 2 indikator tiap baris CSV tersimpan
  - LED pin 3 = SD error indicator
  - Timer1 1Hz for stable ticks (OCR1A)
  - Non-blocking DS conversions, read all 4 each tick
  - CSV uses "OFF" for unreadable sensors; LCD shows OFF where necessary
*/

